'''Adolf Hitler''' (Braunau am Inn, ku ya 20 Mata 1889-Berlin, ku ya 30 Mata 1945) yari umunyagitugu w'Ubudage bw'Abanazi, ukomoka muri Otirishiya na Hongiriya; umuyobozi mukuru w’ibwami kuva 1933 na Führer - umuyobozi - w’Ubudage kuva 1934 kugeza yiyahuye ku gahato. Amaze kugera ku butegetsi yateje jenoside nini ku Bayahudi ndetse n’amoko yose yabonaga ko ari "Umuhumane". Amaherezo yahatiwe kwiyahura ari kumwe na Eva Braun icyarimwe asaba ko bashyingirwa.


